<h1>Welcome to iCARE</h1>

<p>
    iCARE is a web application designed to streamline and manage healthcare-related tasks. Built using the ASP.NET MVC Framework, iCARE allows healthcare providers to manage patient records, assign healthcare workers, and maintain an organized system of care.
</p>

<p>
    This application is part of a group project developed by Team 12, consisting of Kene, Isaiah, Sydney, and Cooper. It uses a dedicated SQL Server database, <strong>Group12_iCAREDB</strong>, to store and manage all essential data.
</p>

<p>
    If you are a registered user, please <a href="@Url.Action("Login")">log in</a> to access the full application.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>Features</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Efficient patient and treatment record management</li>
    <li>Role-based access for admins, doctors, and nurses</li>
    <li>Streamlined workflow for assigning workers to patients</li>
    <li>Detailed document management and record-keeping capabilities</li>
</ul>

